# Force LF line endings for all text files regardless of the runner's
# core.autocrlf setting. The encoder and golden-file tests assume LF;
# Windows GitHub runners default to autocrlf=true and would otherwise
# rewrite checkouts to CRLF, breaking byte-equality assertions.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat these as binary to skip any line-ending or BOM games.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
